# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .gitignore for vouchfx-providers (community index + hosted community providers)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

## .NET build output
bin/
obj/
out/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
artifacts/
publish/
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
project.lock.json

## NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
.nuget/
packages/

## Local pre-release SDK feed — the .nupkg artifacts packed from the engine for
## building against Platform.Sdk before v1.0 is published to nuget.org. The folder
## itself is kept (packages-local/.gitkeep) so the nuget.config source path resolves.
packages-local/*.nupkg
packages-local/*.snupkg

## Test results & coverage
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
*.trx
*.coverage
coverage*.json
coverage*.xml
TestResults/

## IDEs
.vs/
.idea/
*.user
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/extensions.json

## Local secrets & environment
*.secrets
secrets.json
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

## OS / temp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp
*~

## Agent / tooling scratch
.claude/
.serena/

## Pages site build output
_site/
